CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, May 17, 1938, pg. 14 and 15, reads: "Activities Week at Pittsburgh's Y.M.C.A. - Wednesday nite featured the Junior Leaders. (Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of YMCA Junior Leaders, possibly including, standing: Mr. Woodruff on left; kneeling Floyd Allen, and John Etheridge, posed in Centre Avenue YMCA gymnasium
